card.text:
Kicker {4}{W}{W}
Invoke the Angels. (Begin or advance the Path of the Angel.)
If The Angel's Renown was kicked, create a white Avatar creature token with "This creature's power and toughness are each equal to your life total."

Kicker {4}{U}{U}
Invoke the Sphinxes. (Begin or advance the Path of the Sphinx.)
If The Sphinx's Expertise was kicked, exile The Sphinx's Expertise, then take an extra turn after this one. You can't cast nonblue spells during that turn.

Kicker {3}{B}{B}
Invoke the Demons. (Begin or advance the Path of the Demon.)
If The Demon's Covenant was kicked, return up to two target creature cards from your graveyard to your hand, then you may cast a black card from your hand by paying life equal to its mana value rather than paying its mana cost.

Kicker {3}{R}{R}
Invoke the Dragons. (Begin or advance the Path of the Dragon.)
If The Dragon's Majesty was kicked, add eight {R}. You can only cast two more spells this turn.

Kicker {3}{G}{G}
Invoke the Hydras. (Begin or advance the Path of the Hydra.)
If The Hydra's Persistence was kicked, untap up to two target Forests and put four +1/+1 counters on each of them. They become 0/0 green Hydra creatures with trample and hexproof. They're still lands.
